ScheduledFlight - Class in FMS.entities
A scheduled flight in the flight management system (FMS).
ScheduledFlight(ScheduledFlight) - Constructor for class FMS.entities.ScheduledFlight
Creates a deep copy of some original existing scheduled flight.
ScheduledFlight(String, String, String, DateTime, DateTime, int) - Constructor for class FMS.entities.ScheduledFlight
Creates a scheduled flight with an id, an origin, a destination and both departure and arrival as well as distance.
Calls the super constructor.

Staff - Class in FMS.provided
An airline staff member in the flight management system (FMS).
In addition to person details, each airline staff member has a specific role, including, but not limited to, pilot, stewardess, chef de cabin.
Staff(Person, String) - Constructor for class FMS.provided.Staff
Constructs an airline staff member with person data and a role.
Staff(Staff) - Constructor for class FMS.provided.Staff
Constructs a member of airline staff as a (deep) copy of an existing original airline staff member.
Staff(String, String, String, String) - Constructor for class FMS.provided.Staff
Constructs an airline staff member with first and a last name and a passport ID.
